@startuml Watch Event & Recommendation Update -- Sequence Diagram
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam SequenceArrowColor #555555
skinparam SequenceBoxBorderColor #888888

title Watch Event -> Recommendation Update Flow

actor "User" as user
participant "Frontend\n(Next.js)" as fe
participant "API Gateway\n:8080" as gw
participant "Video Service\n:8082" as vs
database "Video DB\n(Supabase)" as videoDb
participant "Outbox Poller" as poller
queue "Kafka" as kafka
participant "Rec Service\n:8083" as rec
database "Rec DB\n(Supabase)" as recDb
participant "Redis Cache" as redis

user -> fe : watches video (plays in player)

note over fe : Frontend tracks watch time\n(every 30s or on video end)
note over fe, vs : Only public READY videos\n(admin-approved for platform uploads)\ncan reach this flow.

fe -> gw : POST /videos/watch\n{ userId, videoId, watchDuration,\n  videoDuration, completionPct }
gw -> vs : forward
vs -> videoDb : INSERT watch_session\n+ UPDATE video.view_count (atomic)\n(same transaction)
vs -> videoDb : INSERT outbox_event\n(topic=video.watched)\n(same transaction)
vs --> gw : 200 OK
gw --> fe : 200 OK

poller -> videoDb : fetch pending outbox_event
poller -> kafka : publish video.watched\n{ eventId, userId, videoId,\n  completionPct, watchDuration,\n  videoDuration, source,\n  timestamp }
poller -> videoDb : mark outbox_event published

kafka -> rec : consume video.watched
rec -> recDb : check processed_events\n(skip if eventId exists)
rec -> rec : compute score\n(completionPct x 1.0, rewatch bonus)
rec -> recDb : INSERT interaction\n{ userId, videoId, score }
rec -> recDb : UPDATE item_factors.view_count\n+ global_score
rec -> rec : update SVD user/item factors\n(incremental update)
rec -> redis : invalidate cache\nfor this userId

note over rec, recDb
  Rewatch detection uses interactions in Rec DB
  as the single source of truth.
end note

note over redis : Next homepage request\nwill recompute fresh\nrecommendations

user -> fe : navigates to homepage

fe -> gw : GET /recommendations/{userId}
gw -> rec : forward
rec -> redis : get cached recs for userId
note right of redis : cache miss\n(was just invalidated)
rec -> rec : run hybrid score:\n  SVD score (0.6 weight)\n  + content-based (0.4 weight)
rec -> redis : cache result (TTL 10 min)
rec --> gw : [ videoId1, videoId2, ... ]
gw --> fe : recommendation list
fe --> user : refreshed homepage feed

@enduml
